{"tid":1236500,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"其實特首辦出面嗰情況無真係咁差","createTime":"2019-06-17T12:25:40.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-17T17:34:35.000Z","uid":67232,"like":539,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":36,"replies":[{"pid":"29a989df6fb74748b5ba3cbaa3a953887b4480ae","tid":1236500,"uid":67232,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T12:25:40.000Z","msg":"雖然得泛民先可以政府set個deadline，但set唔set deadline真係唔係佢地講。<br />\n<br />\n畢竟今次反送中有好多人都係自發出嚟，民陣喺咁多位心目中，都只係個比不反對通知書遊行同埋support嘅人。呢場係一個民眾自發運動，所以佢地set實比人話騎劫同埋收割。<br />\n<br />\n我發夢睇到啦，其實朱凱迪唔係抛翻個波比連登仔就算。佢帶埋支mic同喇吧行入去人群入面，問大家意見，同大家一齊傾個deadline，之後要點算。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">而唔係嗰種:我理撚得你，你哋自己搞撚掂佢嗰種feel</span></span><br />\n<br />\n我知道在場有人有記錄低嘅，可以的話希望可以放上嚟一齊傾，自己傾掂（係難嘅）再掟比泛民。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">意見不合咪一齊傾到掂，而唔係勇武有勇武做，和理非有和理非做，最後喺到互屌</span></span><br />\n<br />\n以下歡迎討論<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3c06c235549ba00958d93621af4fbf3b2f9ddad5","tid":1236500,"uid":117673,"like":198,"dislike":2,"score":196,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T12:27:36.000Z","msg":"我都唔覺得朱凱迪係不負責任 我get到既意思只係佢想大家諗清楚下一步"},{"pid":"07940544833e15f924f029e795d787efcdbba1a2","tid":1236500,"uid":180429,"like":85,"dislike":0,"score":85,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T12:29:12.000Z","msg":"這裏是連登!<br />\n這裏有力量!<br />\n這裏會團結!<br />\n加油香港人!<br />\n加油連登仔!"},{"pid":"87e3a121a87663134cbca4be9e5795909a933bfc","tid":1236500,"uid":67232,"like":57,"dislike":1,"score":56,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T12:30:45.000Z","msg":"據我而家所知，有幾個問題係要諗諗佢。<br />\n<br />\n1.deadline會唔會set喺星期五？因為嗰一日立法會係傾撥款嘅事<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">（有可能係傾東大嶼）</span></span><br />\n<br />\n2.如果set喺星期五，拉埋東大嶼會唔會模糊焦點，同埋流失中間票？<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">因為有d人係支持明日大嶼但唔支持送中</span></span><br />\n<br />\n利申:發夢走咗，淨係記得咁多先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有的話歡迎再加再傾"},{"pid":"9c079d217f01c5758b09ef008082a48270bab6c5","tid":1236500,"uid":67232,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T12:31:01.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b8475e4a80029b0f8e7f1ee83df7208ca16c4c27","tid":1236500,"uid":67232,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T12:31:16.000Z","msg":"自推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"26c20d09db687ce04ba907deb471cd3dc32cbd4a","tid":1236500,"uid":67232,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T12:31:47.000Z","msg":"小弟不才，但希望有人繼續lead落去，一齊討論<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aeb8ab00b4a1a18b0a45eb5af310924e7c2cd540","tid":1236500,"uid":67232,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T12:31:58.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2cd2104b17a8f32cfa9d0e053f7790ed69c799d6","tid":1236500,"uid":67232,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T12:32:59.000Z","msg":"利申唔係泛民打手，只係想香港團結嘅小市民<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a4f26aae9858ea381432301521a7aaac8aefc42d","tid":1236500,"uid":33437,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T12:33:14.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"4011055aff3a66559568e9de54ea64a79188463c","tid":1236500,"uid":67232,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T12:33:52.000Z","msg":"希望咁多位嬲到傻嘅ching，可以喺到留下高見，有計齊齊傾，齊齊度"},{"pid":"673941e3371dda6a0890385f661ae159b1c183d7","tid":1236500,"uid":108337,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"20